name: Wounded Wookiee (V)
Lore: 'When blaster fire from the barge''s gun hit Chewie''s skiff, his leg was injured by shrapnel. This setback distracted the Rebels, causing them to momentarily lose their advantage.',
Text: 'If opponent''s character was just hit during battle, add one destiny to your total power (two if character was a Wookiee); take cards drawn this way into hand. OR If you just lost X Force to a Force drain, draw up to X cards from Reserve Deck.',
